             <a href="/news/georgia-tech-faculty-chosen-chancellors-learning-scholars-program">
              Georgia Tech Faculty Chosen for Chancellor’s Learning Scholars Program
             </a>
            </h3>
            <div class="hg-feed-news-summary">
             <p>
              Four Georgia Tech faculty members were recently selected as Chancellor’s Learning Scholars (CLS) as part of a new program launched by the University System of Georgia (USG).
             </p>
